V.     Differences Between Japan And USA Version

  ARKEDIT Will Auto Scan for the Difference.  The Main Diference is that
  the Japan Version has 32 Levels and the USA Version has 36.  The Only
  other difference is that the main offsets are in different locations. 
  no matter what ARKEDIT will support both versions.

